This will be my last Chelsea Lately upload for the foreseeable future
The new Arsenio Hall show  starts next week and airs the same time as Chelsea and the Daily Show. I get both The Daily Show and Arsenio in HD, so sorry, I will not be recording Chelsea. I will just check out her show between commercials of the other two shows. 

There is another uploader named - verovenlo - that uploads a lot of E shows.
You all could sign in and ask him if he could do some Chelsea for you.
Search for - Below Deck - on the pirate Bay
You could also ask verovenlo about the new Ross Ronny Mathews show called
- Hello Ross - which starts on Friday

Most likely the scene guys will catch up to this and many other talk shows when summer is over.
